name: biocore
body:
biocore is a collection of collaboratively developed software. Many of our projects are available in the [biocore organization](http://github.com/biocore). 

Our larger projects are in their own organizations, including: 

* [QIIME 2](http://github.com/qiime2)
* [Qiita plugins](http://github.com/qiita-spots)
